Turn deprecation into error incorrect initialization of union.

---
struct X
{
    union
    {
        int n;
        float f = 3.14f;  // Error: union field `f` with default initialization `3.14F` must be before field `n`
    }
}

union U
{
    int n;
    float f = 3.14f;  // Error: union field `f` with default initialization `3.14F` must be before field `n`
}
---
